quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  4,114,"MoЖґЖґere alaa e ko heewi e yeewtere maЙ“Й“e nden, si wanaa on yamirЙ—o sadaka, maa moЖґЖґere maa moЖґЖґiЕ‹tingol hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en. Kala waЙ—irЙ—o Й—um Й—aЙ“Й“ugol welayee Alla, arma Men Okka mo njoЙ“di mawndi"
  4,115,"Kala on lunndiiЙ—o NulaaЙ—o on Й“aawo nde paawal ngal Й“anngani mo, o jokki ko wanaa laawol gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en, Men HucciЕ‹tinay mo e kon ko o hucciti, Men Naadoya mo Jahannanma, nge bonii ruttorde"
  4,116,"Pellet, Alla Yawtantaa kafidugol Mo e goЙ—Й—um, Himo Yawtana ko jaasi Й—um wonannde on Mo O Muuyi. Kala on kafiduЙ—o Alla e goЙ—Й—um, gomЙ—ii o majjii majjere woЙ—Й—iinde"
  4,117,"ЖЃe alaa e rewude ko woori Alla, si wanaa [sanamuuji] rewЙ—inaaЙ—i, Й“e alaa e rewude si wanaa seytaane sanndalЙ—iinЙ—o"
  4,118,"Alla HuЙ—ii ndu, ndu wi'i : \"Ma mi jogitoyo e jeyaaЙ“e maa Й“en geЙ“al farlaangal"
  4,119,"ma mi majjinoyЙ“e, ma mi yelinoyЙ“e, ma mi yamiroyЙ“e, ma Й“e taЖґu noppi neemoraaЙ—i Й—in, ma mi yamirЙ“e, ma Й“e waylu tagu Alla ngun !\". Kala jogitiiЙ—o seytaane giЙ—o ko woori Alla, gomЙ—ii o hayrii hayrere Й“anngunde"
  4,120,"Himo foda Й“e himo yelina Й“e, seytaane fodaali Й“e si wanaa hodo"
  4,121,"ЖЃen Й—on wemoolorde maЙ“Й“e nden ko Jahannama, Й“e heЙ“irtaa nge daЙ—irde"
